Lots of changes in this release, and we look forward to your feedback!
- Overhauled the header so that voice and camera search is always just one tap away
- Actions, like sharing and adding bookmarks are now in the header too - behind the "..." button
- Also in the "..." button are the different options to narrow down your search: "News", "Images", "Videos". Many of you mentioned that you'd like these options available, and we listened
- Your stuff (Rewards, Bookmarks, History, Settings) is now just a tap away also. Most of what used to be in the menu on the homepage is now available in the person-like icon in the bottom right corner - from any page!
- With the new tab manager you can easily search for multiple things and keep tabs on all of your searches (including Private tabs)

This update includes a revamped Home page with easy access to voice and camera search, and your feed. The feed will learn what you like to read over time. You can also explicitly dislike a story or the source it came from. Just tap on the "..." icon in the card to take those actions. We also revamped the voice search to be more fun and easy to use.

Looking forward to hearing what you think!

You speak, we listen! We made the following improvements in this release:

• Ability in settings to hide the homepage feed if you don't want to see it by default
• More seamless map and list switching experience for local category searches. Try: "restaurants near me", "movie theaters in Seattle", etc
• Faster loading of webpages - we strive to make Bing the fastest and most beautiful mobile search app
• Various other changes and bug fixes, stability and performance improvements

Thank you for using our app!

Bug Fixes & Improvements:
•Release includes work to improve interaction with VoiceOver, better focus order, contrast for low vision users, and overall fixes to make the experiences easier for everyone to use
•We've made sharing from the app easier by enabling one click access from the top right of search results and site pages
•Improvements to Voice search
•Updates to dark mode to make it more consistent across app screens
•Minor UX fixes and tweaks and many quality and performance improvements

As always, thank you for using Bing Search and providing us with great feedback. Until our next release – The Bing App team
